N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 401.2 - Service program year

State Regulations

The comprehensive annual social services program plan
shall become effective on the first day of October and continue in effect
through the 30th day of September of the next succeeding year. In the event
that the final comprehensive annual social services program plan is not
published on or before the first day of October, the initial effective date
shall be the date of publication. Notes
